Local business information may be displa: Local business information may be displayed when users search for businesses on Google search or Google Maps. Google decides on a per search basis whether to display this information or not and it’s completely automated.
Local Business schema markup enables you: Local Business schema markup enables you to tell Google about your business, including your business name, address and phone number, opening hours and price range. This information may be displayed as a Knowledge Graph card or business carousel.
